---
title: Saucy Veggie Mince & Filo Pastry Pie with Caramelised Onion
description: It’s pie time, but with a new twist to brighten up this classic. The veggie mince is cooked into a tomato filling, packed with beloved veggies like leek. The real surprise, which may be the best one a pie has ever seen, is the sweet and sticky caramelised onions stirred through the filling.

 *This recipe is under 650kcal per serving.*
